    <text type="note" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-09056"> 
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1788-06-01">1788 г. июня 1.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Написать к <persName ref="people.xml#pas02">Пассеку</persName>, чтоб прислал реестр по именам, каких лет и какой нации ученики у <orgName ref="orgs.xml#jesu01">иезуитов</orgName> в <rs ref="orgs.xml#jesu02">Полоцкой</rs> и других <rs ref="orgs.xml#jesu01">сего ордена</rs> школах, и новицияты учатся как давно и с каким успехом.
                <note type="editorial">
                    In 1773 <persName ref="people.xml#cle04">the Pope Clement XIV</persName> banned <orgName ref="orgs.xml#jesu01">the Order of Jesuits</orgName>. Russian Empire did not support this ban and the Jesuits continued to exist on its territory (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#iesuit01">Iesuity v Rossii, s tsarstvovaniia Ekateriny II i do nashego vremeni.</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 20,27.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                    ). In 1780, a novitiate was opened at the <orgName ref="orgs.xml#jesu02">Jesuit College in <placeName ref="places.xml#pol02">Polatsk</placeName></orgName> (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#polots01">Polotskaia akademiia. 1812-1820.</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 36.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                    ).
                </note>
            </p>
        </body>
